    "previewHtml": "<div class=\"accordion\" data-component=\"accordion\">\n  <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n    <h3 class=\"accordion-heading\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"acc-h1\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"acc-p1\" data-component=\"accordion\">\n        아코디언 항목 1\n      </button>\n    </h3>\n    <div class=\"accordion-panel\" id=\"acc-p1\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-h1\">\n      <p>아코디언 패널 1의 내용입니다. 이 영역에 관련 콘텐츠가 표시됩니다.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n    <h3 class=\"accordion-heading\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"acc-h2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"acc-p2\" data-component=\"accordion\">\n        아코디언 항목 2\n      </button>\n    </h3>\n    <div class=\"accordion-panel\" id=\"acc-p2\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-h2\" hidden>\n      <p>아코디언 패널 2의 내용입니다.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n    <h3 class=\"accordion-heading\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"acc-h3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"acc-p3\" data-component=\"accordion\">\n        아코디언 항목 3\n      </button>\n    </h3>\n    <div class=\"accordion-panel\" id=\"acc-p3\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-h3\" hidden>\n      <p>아코디언 패널 3의 내용입니다.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
